The Killer of the Killed
<COREF ID="46" TYPE="IDENT">The most dangerous agreement that disinherits <COREF ID="23" TYPE="IDENT">Iraq</COREF> from <COREF ID="23" TYPE="IDENT">its</COREF> oil resources</COREF> is being signed whilst <COREF ID="12" TYPE="IDENT">the world</COREF> is preoccupied with <COREF ID="0" TYPE="IDENT">the execution of <COREF ID="40" TYPE="IDENT">the Iraqi president Saddam Hussein</COREF></COREF> .
