<COREF ID="46" TYPE="IDENT">The draft</COREF> has been in the possession of <COREF ID="24" TYPE="IDENT">the American government</COREF> for some months according to what <COREF ID="52" TYPE="IDENT">the US Secretary of the Treasury</COREF> said during <COREF ID="52" TYPE="IDENT">his</COREF> visit to Baghdad last autumn .
